name: IOS Developer Account UDID Registration
description: This will make your iDevice eligible for the IOS 7 Beta. Just Purchase, Download the software file, and Upgrade your iDevice. After purchasing use the "Contact" feature at the top of the page and send me your UDID, this is found by going to iTunes on your computer and selecting your iDevice from the Devices. When you see your devices information find where it indicates "Serial Number" and click on it then right click your UDID and copy it. To locate your PayPal Invoice ID which also should be sent along with the UDID check the Email that PayPal has sent to you confirming the payment.
